    <item>
      <title>特朗普集团考虑回购备受关注的酒店</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/trump-organization-eyes-buying-back-dc-hotel-that-drew-criticism</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普集团正就重新收购其位于华盛顿的前酒店进行初步谈判，该酒店曾成为批评者的焦点，他们称唐纳德·特朗普在担任总统期间将其商业和政治利益混为一谈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/trump-organization-eyes-buying-back-dc-hotel-that-drew-criticism</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 16:46:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>塞尔维亚总统武契奇称美国对其唯一炼油厂的制裁非常严厉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/serbia-s-vucic-calls-us-sanctions-on-its-sole-refiner-very-harsh</link>
      <description><![CDATA[塞尔维亚总统亚历山大·武契奇称，美国对塞尔维亚国家石油工业公司（Naftna Industrija Srbije，该国唯一一家由俄罗斯天然气工业股份公司控制的炼油厂）实施制裁的决定非常严厉，并表示需要“某种交易”来确保其正常运转。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/serbia-s-vucic-calls-us-sanctions-on-its-sole-refiner-very-harsh</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 16:28:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登对俄罗斯石油的告别制裁为何意义重大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/why-biden-s-farewell-sanctions-on-russian-oil-are-a-big-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五，美国宣布对俄罗斯石油贸易实施迄今为止最全面、最严厉的制裁，而就在十天之前，乔·拜登将离开白宫，由唐纳德·特朗普接任总统。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/why-biden-s-farewell-sanctions-on-russian-oil-are-a-big-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 16:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>委内瑞拉总统马杜罗上任后美国加大施压</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/us-raises-pressure-on-venezuela-s-maduro-as-he-starts-new-term</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国周五加大了对委内瑞拉总统尼古拉斯·马杜罗及其政权的压力，包括提高逮捕涉嫌贩毒分子的悬赏金额，并对官员实施新的制裁，以回应其有争议的选举和对反对派的镇压。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/us-raises-pressure-on-venezuela-s-maduro-as-he-starts-new-term</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 15:33:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国制裁塞尔维亚唯一一家由俄罗斯天然气工业股份公司控制的炼油厂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/us-sanctions-serbia-s-sole-refiner-controlled-by-gazprom</link>
      <description><![CDATA[作为针对俄罗斯能源生产商的新一轮全面制裁措施的一部分，美国财政部对塞尔维亚唯一一家由俄罗斯天然气工业股份公司 (Gazprom) 控制的炼油企业 Naftna Industrija Srbije 实施了制裁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/us-sanctions-serbia-s-sole-refiner-controlled-by-gazprom</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 15:28:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国加大对俄罗斯能源制裁压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/us-increases-pressure-on-russia-with-sweeping-energy-sanctions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普上任后，拜登政府正在寻找最后一刻的方法来提升乌克兰在可能的和平谈判中的筹码，美国对俄罗斯石油工业实施了迄今为止最严厉的制裁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/us-increases-pressure-on-russia-with-sweeping-energy-sanctions</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 15:18:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大外交部长乔利不会竞选接替特鲁多</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/canada-foreign-minister-joly-won-t-enter-race-to-replace-trudeau</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大外交部长梅拉妮乔利表示，她不会参加继任贾斯汀特鲁多担任总理的竞选。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/canada-foreign-minister-joly-won-t-enter-race-to-replace-trudeau</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 15:14:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普在封口费案中被定罪后未受到惩罚</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/trump-s-sentencing-in-hush-money-criminal-case-begins-in-ny</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普是首位被判重罪的前美国总统，纽约一名法官在其封口费案中判处他无需入狱，但他本月仍将带着犯罪记录返回白宫。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/trump-s-sentencing-in-hush-money-criminal-case-begins-in-ny</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 14:37:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>委内瑞拉反对派抓住希望，马杜罗巩固权力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/maduro-cements-power-in-venezuela-as-opposition-grasps-for-hope</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在竞争对手四散而去、举步维艰的情况下，委内瑞拉总统尼古拉斯·马杜罗宣誓就任第三个六年总统，无视国际社会对其虚假选举和残酷镇压异见的谴责。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/maduro-cements-power-in-venezuela-as-opposition-grasps-for-hope</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 12:04:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>因加沙战争，土耳其将连续第二年抵制达沃斯</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/turkey-set-to-boycott-davos-for-second-year-over-war-in-gaza</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其总统雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安将延长该国因加沙战争而抵制达沃斯世界经济论坛一年，高级经济官员也将缺席本月的论坛。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/turkey-set-to-boycott-davos-for-second-year-over-war-in-gaza</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 11:29:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
